    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/ddb9edb8f06668b8c2d52aa26a5ff9d3.poster.avif?t=1770798281\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/ddb9edb8f06668b8c2d52aa26a5ff9d3.webm?t=1770798281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/ddb9edb8f06668b8c2d52aa26a5ff9d3.mp4?t=1770798281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Go North》</strong>是一场舒适而又身临其境的迷宫冒险。借助众多魔法和科技道具，你将穿越精美独特的迷宫，探索浩瀚无垠的世界，开启一段前所未有的故事驱动型冒险之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/ef6e185d2b3b6606563e096233ebd87b.poster.avif?t=1770798281\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/ef6e185d2b3b6606563e096233ebd87b.webm?t=1770798281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/ef6e185d2b3b6606563e096233ebd87b.mp4?t=1770798281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >据说迷宫之神居住在世界的最北端，他会满足任何勇敢机智的冒险者到达他那里后的一个愿望。但要想真正到达北方，你必须穿越无数由迷宫制造者精心设计、让你迷失方向的复杂迷宫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/4cb2c7db155cee69f94b8c772a1490ec.poster.avif?t=1770798281\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/4cb2c7db155cee69f94b8c772a1490ec.webm?t=1770798281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041730/extras/4cb2c7db155cee69f94b8c772a1490ec.mp4?t=1770798281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >达拉踏上旅程，只有一个目标：拜见迷宫之神，实现她永恒的愿望。然而，似乎有某种邪恶的魔物正在腐蚀迷宫。某种东西……或者某个人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以第三人称视角探索美丽的迷宫：漫步于氛围优美、美轮美奂的迷宫中，探索不同的物品、角色、谜题和故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找、保存并使用独特实用的物品：每个迷宫中散落着各种不同的物品，从简单的停车标志到功能更强大的机器人老鼠，应有尽有，它们会快速奔向出口</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开谜题，避开障碍：运用你的智慧，解开每个迷宫中的各种谜题和障碍。解开不同的谜语和线索，发现秘密通道、物品和彩蛋。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人游戏：与你的好友和全球玩家跨平台在线对战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街机游戏：探索无数精心生成的、形态各异、世界各异的迷宫。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
